    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2088070/extras/71db7579532649465f9585c04e3739d8.avif?t=1665153061\" width=460 height=214 /></span><br>猎手们，拯救这个被感染的世界！坚持黄金3分钟，一起迎接黎明的到来！！！交流攻略心得，可加入官方QQ群：485462136<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >【游戏介绍】</h2><strong>《僵尸猎手-幸存者》</strong>是一款以末日环境猎杀僵尸为主题的<strong>Roguelike式</strong>休闲游戏，首发角色只有一条弹道，攻击属性并不出色。每层通关选择Buff强化角色，搭配自己的技能和Buff组合路线，从刮痧到无敌！关卡中的怪物会不断冲向角色，怪物的数量和强度会随着每层的等级而增加，每层难度等级需要在3分钟内清除所有僵尸！据说没有人能挑战到超过200层的难度等级。。。你的极限能坚持到第几层难度？？！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >【技能操作】</h2>主动技能<strong> Q </strong>：<strong>怒气爆发</strong> ，集满怒气条即可释放，每次释放怒气后，叠加下一次怒气基础伤害！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2088070/extras/4df7b7a2338011273e5c2b3b6d1070f7.poster.avif?t=1665153061\" width=616 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2088070/extras/4df7b7a2338011273e5c2b3b6d1070f7.webm?t=1665153061\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2088070/extras/4df7b7a2338011273e5c2b3b6d1070f7.mp4?t=1665153061\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>主动技能<strong> E </strong>：<strong>死亡杂技</strong> ，以角色自身为中心扩大飞镖攻击范围并保持一定的时间，需集齐3把飞镖可学习该技能，每集齐3把、5把可解锁转速特技！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2088070/extras/5b93ddcc63b95326927ee26c6bb31535.poster.avif?t=1665153061\" width=616 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2088070/extras/5b93ddcc63b95326927ee26c6bb31535.webm?t=1665153061\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2088070/extras/5b93ddcc63b95326927ee26c6bb31535.mp4?t=1665153061\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2088070/extras/ca023544130038f25879726fcb5c0d87.poster.avif?t=1665153061\" width=616 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2088070/extras/ca023544130038f25879726fcb5c0d87.webm?t=1665153061\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2088070/extras/ca023544130038f25879726fcb5c0d87.mp4?t=1665153061\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >【游戏特点】</h2>每个Buff种类都有不同的品级，分别为：绿色，蓝色，紫色，橙色，红色，彩色，品级顺序从低到高，彩色品级是最高品级也是最稀有的Buff。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2088070/extras/d4dfa5a9476d23b8608f7cfc7c62e6eb.avif?t=1665153061\" width=616 height=345 /></span><br>每5层，会出现超级BOSS，击杀超级BOSS以获得额外技能宝箱，获得技能宝箱越多，攻击方式越丰富，解锁更多极致解压的体验！！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2088070/extras/394bc6e0bbfd58e4e1e51865c95031ce.poster.avif?t=1665153061\" width=616 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2088070/extras/394bc6e0bbfd58e4e1e51865c95031ce.webm?t=1665153061\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2088070/extras/394bc6e0bbfd58e4e1e51865c95031ce.mp4?t=1665153061\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >让人深思的搭配</h2>在每层通关之后，都会刷出Buff供玩家自由挑选，尤其前期的Buff属性搭配思路极为重要，通关层级数量越多Buff叠加越劲爆！<br>（每层通关选择Buff时，可以使用金币刷新出品级更高的Buff，也可以在个人属性中选择前面任意关卡进行重洗覆盖Buff）<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2088070/extras/921cffc516bd400f59ff02d01c5957c7.poster.avif?t=1665153061\" width=616 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2088070/extras/921cffc516bd400f59ff02d01c5957c7.webm?t=1665153061\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2088070/extras/921cffc516bd400f59ff02d01c5957c7.mp4?t=1665153061\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >轻松有趣的玩法</h2>游戏以快速刷新快速攻击的战斗为主体，让玩家每个层级都是<strong>肉鸽</strong>+射击的乐趣体验，让你直接射爆爽爆！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2088070/extras/97f8e8ddc4ad0f23b301dfedac4250db.poster.avif?t=1665153061\" width=616 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2088070/extras/97f8e8ddc4ad0f23b301dfedac4250db.webm?t=1665153061\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2088070/extras/97f8e8ddc4ad0f23b301dfedac4250db.mp4?t=1665153061\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2088070/extras/5b4b99ab795ca73e444d5cf42334fff8.poster.avif?t=1665153061\" width=616 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2088070/extras/5b4b99ab795ca73e444d5cf42334fff8.webm?t=1665153061\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2088070/extras/5b4b99ab795ca73e444d5cf42334fff8.mp4?t=1665153061\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >独树一帜的风格</h2>游戏以僵尸题材的恐怖氛围，难度等级为300层，每个层级3分钟，搭配史诗及配乐，个性突出！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >【游戏背景】</h2>公元2065年，邪恶生物研究博士哈德从传说中的吸血鬼英公爵菲利斯抽取生物基因进行科学研究，并在3年后取得惊人效用，研究成果的不老基因原作用时减慢细胞衰老速度，让担心渐渐走向生命尽头的各地富豪趋之若鹜，哈德博士并因此获得了当年的恒星研究奖，一时风头无人能及。<br>但哈德并不满足于此，完美主义的他想再进一步提升效果，渐渐失控的他开始使用活人进行研究，并掌握了其中的奥秘，本以为是他认为最完美的一剂基因药，却出现了一个极为恐怖的副作用，那就是意识失控与传染，哈德再也无法控制基因药的意识失控，最终扑向了一名助手并对其撕咬，本应立刻死亡的助手却在3小时重新站立了起来，并感染了更多的人。。。<br>雷曼作为保卫队队长，奉命封锁并清理诺曼底的所有丧尸，他的技术支持者艾莉则源源不断的提供强化人类生命活性的基因药，战斗由此展开！",
